text: Talulah Jane Riley-MilburnBirths, Marriages & Deaths Index of England & Wales, 1916-2005; Ancestry.com; accessed 3 November 2015. (born 26 September 1985), known professionally as Talulah Riley, is an English actress. She has appeared in movies such as Pride & Prejudice, St Trinian's, The Boat That Rocked, St Trinian's 2: The Legend of Fritton's Gold, and Inception. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from Hertfordshire
